SECTION_CONTENT:
Handling
Storage
Do not breathe dust. Do not breathe vapors or spray mist. Do not get in eyes, on skin, or on
clothing. Handle under inert gas, protect from moisture. Use only under a chemical fume
hood.
Keep in a dry, cool and well-ventilated place. Keep container tightly closed. Keep away
from direct sunlight.
